<h2>New taxi ranks</h2>
<p>If you have a suggestion for a new taxi rank, then you can send this to us by <a href="mailto:tphranksinterchange&#64;tfl.gov.uk">emailing Taxi and Private Hire</a>. </p>
<p>When you email us please include the following information:</p>
<ul>
    <li>The specific location</li>
    <li>Whether the location is on the red route, a borough road or private property</li>
    <li>What the taxi rank would serve (such as a hotel, nightclub, station etc)</li>
    <li>A photo of the location</li>
    <li>Any other relevant information</li>
</ul>
<p>We'll consider your request and if we think this is feasible we'll contact the relevant highway authority or land owner, so they can also consider this.</p>
